user.about:
hi everyone :) my name is ryley!

i am in the process downsizing certain areas of my life in order to save towards future goals. this includes freeing up some closet space in hopes of saving for tuition and a future vehicle purchase! i would really appreciate the support!

all clothes are in great/relatively untouched condition (unless otherwise mentioned) and come from a smoke-free household. all clothes will also be freshly cleaned and ironed before shipping.

i am open to a certain degree of bargaining, but all items are cross-referenced with similar items found on the site in order to assure fair pricing from the get-go :) i am also open to potential trades.

if an item appears as reserved, i will not be accepting counter offers of a higher price out of respect for the first person interested. if you favorite the item, however, i will make sure to message you with updates in the event that the item becomes available again :)

deals include:
~ buy 2 marked items and receive a 3rd 50% off! marked items are indicated by a <3 in the description of the item
~ purchases over $20 receive a bonus gift as a thank you for your support

thank you so much for visiting my site, have a great day! :)
